metadata.name: On The Beach - Lady Gaga Meets Rainer Maria Rilke
metadata.description:
On The Beach
                                   by Rainer Maria Rilke

Past the tide.
Still it roars far away.
Wild water and above
Star to star.

Who saw it well,
O blessed land,
How the wave
Overcame.

It still roars far away.
The night wind brings
Memory and a wave
Runs in the sand.

1/1 handpainted, digital painting

Creator Barbara Johanna Billeiter alias Duckylemon.
